| `backend/app/domain/astrology/runtime/aspect_calculation_contracts.py` / `AspectDefinitionRuntimeData` | `default_valence`, `interpretive_valence`, `energy_type` | Contrat legacy de transition qui expose des vues separees. | Temporary; sortie apres suppression dediee du contrat legacy. |
| `backend/app/domain/astrology/runtime/aspect_runtime_data.py` / `AspectInterpretationRuntimeData` | `default_valence`, `interpretive_valence`, `energy_type` | Projection legacy bornee d'indices interpretatifs. | Temporary; sortie apres migration des consommateurs legacy. |
| `backend/app/domain/astrology/runtime/aspect_runtime_data.py` / `AspectInterpretiveHintsRuntimeData` | `default_valence`, `interpretive_valence`, `energy_type`, `interpretive_weight` | Hints interpretatifs types pour adapters et prompts, sans recalcul structurel. | Permanent. |
| `backend/app/domain/astrology/runtime/runtime_reference.py` / `AspectReferenceData` | `default_valence`, `interpretive_valence`, `energy_type` | Payload referentiel legacy scinde ensuite en vues structurelle et interpretative. | Temporary; sortie apres migration DB/referentiel dediee. |
